    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until slightly softened</p>",
