      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your<strong> orzo</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the orzo for 6-8 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>orzo</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
