    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad </strong>and your<strong> spinach</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the tomatoes have softened slightly, add your<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong> to the pan and stir it all together</p>",
