    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spinach is starting to wilt, add your <strong>pesto</strong> with your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and<strong> tomato paste</strong></p><p>Crumble <strong>half</strong> your <strong>goats' cheese</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) directly into the pan</p><p>Add the <strong>cooked orzo</strong> with a small splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and mix until thoroughly combined – this is your <strong>goat’s cheese, tomato & pesto orzo</strong></p>",
