    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> goats’ cheese, tomato & pesto orzo</strong> topped with your <strong>pine nuts</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong>, then crumble your <strong>remaining goats’ cheese</strong> on top</p><p>Serve the<strong> salad</strong> to the side topped with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
